  "texts": [
    "To this end, we created a comprehensive and large DFU dataset using our proposed data collection protocol.",
    "We called this DFU dataset, the Zivot dataset, to honour the hard work and assistance of Zivot Limb Preservation Centre clinicians, nurses and staff in gathering this database.",
    "Our main contributions are• We created a novel, comprehensive and large DFU multimodal dataset using our proposed data collection protocol.",
    "• Our data collection protocol was meticulously developed with expert clinical and research insights to be adopted as a gold standard for future DFU data collection.",
    "• We showed the benefits of this dataset in a conventional DFU-related DL method."
  ],
